para_trans: New health sub-centre sanctioned at Nanded
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No.287 / Health-4
Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Mumbai: J. No. AASE / Rooms-7A / T-6 /
Kotbazar / Upke / Manzoor / Nanded / 2968-70/2024, Dy. Letter of 8.8.2024.
To sanction a new health sub-centre at Mauje Kotbazar, Taluka Kandahar, District Nanded.
Approval was under consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Special for sanctioning new Health Sub-centre at Mauje Kotbazar, Taluka Kandahar, District Nanded
The matter is being approved by the government.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
